#Predict using differencing
prev_pred <- t(df_atleast_50cts[1:42, 1:198])
pred <- c()
errors <- 0
error_arr <- c()
fitted_val <- c()
for (i in c(1:6)) {
  diff <- c(predict(var_model, n.ahead = i, newxreg = prev_pred, ncol=42))
  curr_pred <- prev_pred + diff
  act <- df_atleast_50cts[1:42, 198 + i]
  error_arr <- c(error_arr, c(curr_pred - act))
  fitted_val <- c(fitted_val, curr_pred)
  error <- sum((curr_pred - act) ^ 2)
  errors <- errors + error
  prev_pred <- t(df_atleast_50cts[1:42, 1+i:198+i])
}
